Supreme Court, Appellate Term, June, 1898.

Before Beekman, P. J., Gildersleeve and Giegerich, JJ.

Kate Clokey as Administratrix, etc., of John T. Clokey, deceased, Respondent, v. The International Rubber Clothing & General Supply Co., Appellant Appeal from a judgment of the General Term of the City Court affirming a judgment in favor of plaintiff. William Stuart for Appellant; Robinson, Biddle & Ward for Respondent.

Judgment affirmed, with costs; no opinion.
